#. Plugin Name of the plugin
#: nudge.php
msgid "Nudge - Free Shipping Progress Bar for WooCommerce"
msgstr "Nudge - Barra de progreso de envío gratuita para WooCommerce"

#. Plugin URI of the plugin
#: nudge.php
msgid "https://plogins.com/nudge/"
msgstr "https://plogins.com/es/nudge/"

#. Description of the plugin
#: nudge.php
msgid ""
"Show a free-shipping progress bar that nudges shoppers to add more to their "
"cart."
msgstr ""
"Muestre una barra de progreso de envío gratuito que impulse a los "
"compradores a añadir más a su carrito."

#. Author of the plugin
#: nudge.php
msgid "WPPoland"
msgstr "WPPoland"

#. Author URI of the plugin
#: nudge.php
msgid "https://plogins.com/"
msgstr "https://plogins.com/"

#: nudge.php:47
msgid ""
"Nudge - Free Shipping Progress Bar for WooCommerce requires WooCommerce to "
"be active."
msgstr ""
"Nudge: la barra de progreso de envío gratuito para WooCommerce requiere que "
"WooCommerce esté activo."

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:41
msgid "Nudge: Free Shipping Bar"
msgstr "Nudge: barra de envío gratuito"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:42
msgid "Nudge"
msgstr "Nudge"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:103
msgid ""
"Nudge shows customers how close they are to free shipping and exactly how "
"much more to add to unlock it. It updates live as the cart changes. The "
"defaults work out of the box, adjust below only if you want to."
msgstr ""
"Nudge muestra a los clientes qué tan cerca están del envío gratuito y "
"exactamente cuánto más añadir para desbloquearlo. Se actualiza en vivo a "
"medida que cambia el carrito. Los valores predeterminados funcionan de "
"inmediato, ajústelos a continuación solo si lo desea."

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:110
msgid "General"
msgstr "General"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:111
msgid ""
"Turn the bar on and choose where shoppers see it. Showing it on both cart "
"and checkout keeps the goal in front of them through the whole purchase."
msgstr ""
"Encienda la barra y elija dónde la ven los compradores. Mostrarlo tanto en "
"el carrito como en el pago mantiene el objetivo frente a ellos durante toda "
"la compra."

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:115
msgid "Enable Nudge"
msgstr "Habilitar Nudge"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:119
msgid "Show the free-shipping progress bar to shoppers."
msgstr "Muestre la barra de progreso del envío gratuito a los compradores."

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:121
msgid ""
"When off, the bar and its assets never load, no styles or scripts are added "
"to the front end."
msgstr ""
"Cuando está desactivada, la barra y sus recursos nunca se cargan, no se "
"agregan estilos ni scripts al front-end."

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:125
msgid "Cart page"
msgstr "Página del carrito"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:125
msgid "Show the bar on the cart page, above the totals."
msgstr "Muestra la barra en la página del carrito, encima de los totales."

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:126
msgid "Checkout page"
msgstr "página de pago"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:126
msgid "Show the bar on checkout, so the goal stays visible while they pay."
msgstr ""
"Muestre la barra al finalizar la compra, para que el objetivo permanezca "
"visible mientras pagan."

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:133
msgid "Free-shipping threshold"
msgstr "Umbral de envío gratuito"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:134
msgid ""
"Where the “you reach free shipping at…” amount comes from. Automatic keeps "
"the bar in sync with your real shipping rules, so it is never wrong after a "
"price change."
msgstr ""
"De dónde viene el importe «consigues el envío gratis a partir de…». "
"Automático mantiene la barra sincronizada con sus reglas de envío reales, "
"para que nunca se equivoque tras un cambio de precio."

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:139
msgid "Threshold source"
msgstr "Fuente umbral"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:146
msgid "Automatic (from free-shipping method)"
msgstr "Automático (desde método de envío gratuito)"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:147
msgid "Manual (fixed amount)"
msgstr "Manual (cantidad fija)"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:156
msgid ""
"Automatic reads the minimum order amount from your WooCommerce free-shipping"
" method, the smallest one across your shipping zones, so the bar updates "
"itself when you change that rule. The manual amount below is used as a "
"fallback when no such method is found."
msgstr ""
"Automático lee el monto mínimo del pedido de su método de envío gratuito de "
"WooCommerce, el más pequeño en sus zonas de envío, por lo que la barra se "
"actualiza sola cuando cambia esa regla. La cantidad manual a continuación se"
" utiliza como alternativa cuando no se encuentra dicho método."

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:161
msgid "Manual amount"
msgstr "Cantidad manual"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:165
msgid ""
"In your store currency, before shipping and taxes. Used when the source is "
"Manual, or as the fallback for Automatic. Default: 50."
msgstr ""
"En la moneda de tu tienda, antes de envío e impuestos. Se utiliza cuando la "
"fuente es Manual o como alternativa para Automático. Predeterminado: 50."

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:173
msgid "Messages"
msgstr "Mensajes"

#. translators: %s: the {amount} token, shown as a styled chip.
#: src/Admin/Settings.php:178
#, php-format
msgid ""
"What the bar says before and after the goal is reached. Write %s where you "
"want the remaining amount, it is replaced with the value formatted in your "
"store currency (e.g. $12.00)."
msgstr ""
"Lo que dice la barra antes y después de alcanzar la meta. Escriba %s donde "
"desee el monto restante; se reemplazará con el valor formateado en la moneda"
" de su tienda (por ejemplo, $12,00)."

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:187
msgid "Progress message"
msgstr "Mensaje de progreso"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:192 src/Admin/Settings.php:204
msgid "Shoppers see:"
msgstr "Los compradores ven:"

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:199
msgid "Success message"
msgstr "Mensaje de éxito"

#: templates/progress-bar.php:42
msgid "Progress towards free shipping"
msgstr "Progreso hacia el envío gratuito"
